lead_paragraph: Jeff Green scored 29 points, Marc Gasol had 22 points, six rebounds and five assists, and the Memphis Grizzlies thwarted a fourth-quarter rally to defeat the Sacramento Kings 121-117 on Saturday night.

headline.print_headline: Green Scores 29, Gasol 22 as Grizzlies Defeat Kings 121-117
